---
// Kontakt (§7.12) — poptávkový formulář.
// Formulář je připraven pro Netlify Forms (atribut data-netlify="true").
// Při hostingu na Vercel/Cloudflare nahraď action za Formspree endpoint
// nebo napojení na vlastní SMTP.
---

<section id="kontakt" class="section bg-navy text-white">
  <div class="container-tight grid gap-14 lg:grid-cols-2">
    <div class="reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow !text-gold-light">Kontakt</span>
      <h2 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-bold sm:text-4xl">Domluvme si ukázku</h2>
      <p class="mt-5 text-lg text-white/70">
        Ukážeme vám kiosek, AI asistenta i administraci na reálném scénáři vašeho provozu.
        Nezávazně a bez instalace.
      </p>

      <ul class="mt-8 space-y-4 text-white/80">
        <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-white/5 text-xl">✉️</span>
          <a href="mailto:info@recepceai.cz" class="hover:text-gold-light">info@recepceai.cz</a>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-white/5 text-xl">🌐</span>
          <span>recepceai.cz</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-white/5 text-xl">🛎️</span>
          <span>Chytrá recepce pro hotely, penziony a ubytovny</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal" style="transition-delay:100ms">
      <form
        name="poptavka"
        method="POST"
        action="/api/contact"
        class="rounded-3xl bg-white/[0.04] p-7 shadow-2xl ring-1 ring-white/10 backdrop-blur"
      >
        <p class="hidden" aria-hidden="true">
          <label>Nevyplňujte: <input name="bot-field" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" /></label>
        </p>

        <div class="grid gap-5 sm:grid-cols-2">
          <label class="block">
            <span class="text-sm font-medium text-white/80">Jméno a příjmení *</span>
            <input
              type="text" name="jmeno" required autocomplete="name"
              class="mt-1.5 w-full rounded-xl border border-white/15 bg-white/5 px-4 py-3 text-white placeholder-white/40 outline-none transition focus:border-gold focus:bg-white/10"
              placeholder="Jan Novák"
            />
          </label>
          <label class="block">
            <span class="text-sm font-medium text-white/80">Provozovna</span>
            <input
              type="text" name="provozovna" autocomplete="organization"
              class="mt-1.5 w-full rounded-xl border border-white/15 bg-white/5 px-4 py-3 text-white placeholder-white/40 outline-none transition focus:border-gold focus:bg-white/10"
              placeholder="Hotel / penzion"
            />
          </label>
          <label class="block">
            <span class="text-sm font-medium text-white/80">E-mail *</span>
            <input
              type="email" name="email" required autocomplete="email"
              class="mt-1.5 w-full rounded-xl border border-white/15 bg-white/5 px-4 py-3 text-white placeholder-white/40 outline-none transition focus:border-gold focus:bg-white/10"
              placeholder="vas@email.cz"
            />
          </label>
          <label class="block">
            <span class="text-sm font-medium text-white/80">Telefon</span>
            <input
              type="tel" name="telefon" autocomplete="tel"
              class="mt-1.5 w-full rounded-xl border border-white/15 bg-white/5 px-4 py-3 text-white placeholder-white/40 outline-none transition focus:border-gold focus:bg-white/10"
              placeholder="+420 …"
            />
          </label>
        </div>

        <label class="mt-5 block">
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-white/80">Zpráva</span>
          <textarea
            name="zprava" rows="4"
            class="mt-1.5 w-full resize-none rounded-xl border border-white/15 bg-white/5 px-4 py-3 text-white placeholder-white/40 outline-none transition focus:border-gold focus:bg-white/10"
            placeholder="Kolik máte pokojů / jednotek a co potřebujete vyřešit?"
          ></textarea>
        </label>

        <label class="mt-4 flex items-start gap-2.5 text-sm text-white/60">
          <input type="checkbox" name="souhlas" required class="mt-1 h-4 w-4 rounded border-white/20 bg-white/5 accent-gold" />
          <span>Souhlasím se zpracováním údajů za účelem vyřízení poptávky (GDPR).</span>
        </label>

        <button type="submit" class="btn-primary mt-6 w-full">🛎️ Odeslat poptávku</button>
        <p class="mt-3 text-center text-xs text-white/45">Ozveme se obvykle do jednoho pracovního dne.</p>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
